    STATEMENT OF ASSETS, LIABILITIES AND EXPENSES 
</h3>
<p style="text-align:center;padding:0px;margin:0px;">
    under section 80(1) of the Income Tax Ordinance, 1984 (XXXVI of 1984)
</p>

<table style="border: 1px solid; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
    <tr>
        <td>
