                <li>
                    If your spouse or  minor children and dependent(s) are not assessee, you have to include their assets and liabilities in your statement;  
                </li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 0">
                    Schedule 25 is the integral part of this Statement if you have business capital or agriculture or non-agricultural property. Provide additional papers if necessary.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>

